Hi {!Contact.FirstName},
We’re pleased to advise that the sample Label and Order Summary you provided has been validated and complies with our minimum standards.
Your unique 10 digit account number is: XXXXXXXXXX
We want to make this as easy as possible for you, so we’ve attached a step-by-step guide on how to register and access the Australia Post Shipping and Tracking APIs.

We’re here to help, so if you have any questions get in touch with us at customer_connectivity@auspost.com.au.
Regards
Lodgement & APIs Team
Parcels, eCommerce and Digital
